<TD WIDTH=460 COLSPAN=2 VALIGN="TOP"><H3><i>Power Semiconductors for Battery-Operated Electronics</i></H3><p>
IR has staffed a new group to develop products to serve the needs of customers that design 
portable, battery-operated electronics. This group, termed the Battery Management Group, is 
delivering miniature and efficient power semiconductors that feature Generation 5 HEXFET<sup>®</sup> power 
MOSFETs, low V<sub>f</sub> Schottky rectifiers and highly integrated solid-state relays. Increasingly, these 
devices are developed as part of a complete power system design to speed your design cycles. 
Whether you're looking for system solutions or a specific power device,  IR's Battery Management 
Group will develop the products that will help you meet your design needs.<p>
See below for related links to assist you with Design Support, News Releases and Quick Links to related
Battery-Operated Electronic pages.
</TD>
</TR>
